OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother very warm day, dry and
OL,6,Fpredominantly sunny, the sunshine may
OL,7,Fturn hazy at times with the passage of
OL,8,Fhigh-level cloud. Cooler along coastal
OL,9,Fareas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBecoming cloudy overnight
OL,12,Fwith low cloud and fog coming off the
OL,13,FNorth Sea and spreading slowly
OL,14,Fwestwards by the morning. Temperatures
OL,15,Fremaining warm overnight but cooler
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
